      • removeObsoleteFolders

        protected boolean removeObsoleteFolders​(org.apache.sling.api.resource.Resource resource)
                                 throws org.apache.sling.api.resource.PersistenceException
        Scans the resource tree below topresource for AssetsConstants.NODE_TYPE_RENDITIONs and returns true if there is one or false if there isn't. Subresources are removed if they do not contain a rendition; subresources of a rendition are not checked.
        Throws:
        org.apache.sling.api.resource.PersistenceException
